<h3 id="running-scummvm-from-command-line">Running ScummVM from command line</h3>
<p>The simplest way to run a game from the command line is to type:</p>

<div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>scummvm samnmax
</code></pre></div></div>
